Class RestAssuredTestCaseWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.testwriter.TestCaseContentWriter
      • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.restassured.RestAssuredTestCaseWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TestCaseWriter

    public class RestAssuredTestCaseWriter
extends TestCaseContentWriter
    Writes the source code for REST Assured test cases that execute API requests.
